The '''''Spinner''''' was a [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]]. In [[19 BBY/Legends|19.9 BBY]], after a stop at [[Orleon]], it was infested with [[Stone mite/Legends|stone mites]]. On approach to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] [[Westport]], it crashed at [[Kishi]] and released its mite cargo.

